name: TOYIN TOMATO STILL
description: Inspired by a  Popular Nigerian drama series. The name of the lady was Toyin and her admirer would tease her saying she is as fresh as a tomato and when she blushes her face turns to the color of the tomato.so her admirer called her Toyin Tomato .I wanted to do a food art , the name came to my mind like a prompt and i did this.. The art  is like a tribute to the pretty lady in the play or drama series and to all the beautiful ladies  out there..
